          <p class='first-para'>
            Does the noble Baroness agree that the normal meaning in the English language of 50 per cent plus one is that you get a simple majority? It is not 50 per cent of those entitled to vote.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0662P0-01992'>
        <a name='S5LV0662P0_20040609_GCR_168'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-doreen-miller' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0662P0_20040609_GCR_168' title='Link to this speech by Ms Doreen Miller' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
